<section id="homepageBanner">


    <h1 id="homepageLogo">MNMLIST</h1>
    <p id="tagline">Share your (wunder)lists with anyone.</p>
    <%= link_to "Connect with Wunderlist", user_wunderlist_omniauth_authorize_path, id: "callToAction" %>



</section>
<section id="homepageDescription">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="paragraph-center">
      <article>
        <h2>Just three steps</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Choose a list</li>
          <li>Click on share and get the shareable url</li>
          <li>Send the url to your friends or community</li>
        </ol>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="paragraph-center">
      <article class="container">
        <p>They will see something like this:</p>
        <%= image_tag "screenshot_movies.png", class: "example-image" %>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="paragraph-center">
      <article>
        <h2>More features soon...</h2>
        <p>Sharing a list is a missing feature on Wunderlist. I hope you'll enjoy using this tool and share lots of lists with your friends. I plan to add more features, like accessing the note inside a list item, and a lists discovery...</p>
        <p>If you have any feedbacks or issues, please feel free to contact me: <%= mail_to "dim@mnmlist.io" %> / <%= link_to "@dimitribosch", "https://twitter.com/dimitribosch" %></p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
